title: 8 Iconic Things From ‘90s Hip Hop Music Videos You Can Still See in New York City
text:
8 Iconic Things From ‘90s Hip Hop Music Videos You Can Still See in New York City This will put you in a vintage New York state of mind. by VH1 33m ago 
By Marcus Reeves 
The landscape of New York City’s hip hop history has really changed over the decades. This map supports us on that fact. But quite a few places and spaces and rituals still can be seen around town. Particularly those things that have been captured via ‘90s hip hop music videos. Here’s a look at those things from ‘90s hip hop music videos that can still be witnessed today. 
Watch what happens when Barry Fouray tries to sign on as Ahm’s manager and make sure to tune in to The Breaks on Monday night at 9/8c on VH1.
